## Architecture

```
                Data Source
                     │
                     ▼
             Amazon S3 (Raw Data)
                     │
                     ▼
          AWS Lambda / AWS Glue
        (Processing & Transformation)
                     │
                     ▼
          Processed Data Storage
                     │
                     ▼
      Athena / Database / Analytics
                     │
                     ▼
            Reports & Insights
```

