## Workflow

1. Data is uploaded or generated.
2. Files are stored in Amazon S3.
3. AWS services process the incoming data.
4. Processed data is stored for analysis.
5. Monitoring captures execution logs and performance metrics.
6. Results can be queried or visualized for business insights.

